    "m_Title": "9. Non-constant movement (3)",
    "m_Content": "Multiply the Sine output with the wind scaling factor we computed in 8. Instead of the Sine output, we will feed this into the z component of the Combine.\nCheck out the result in Scene mode and come back.",
